 Phase 5: Deployment Automation

 5.1 Deployment Script

 Create: /var/www/gema/deploy.sh

 Features:
 - Pull latest code from git
 - Backend: Build + PM2 reload (zero-downtime)
 - Frontend: Build + copy to Nginx directory + clear cache
 - Usage: ./deploy.sh [backend|frontend|all]

 chmod +x /var/www/gema/deploy.sh

 5.2 Health Check Monitoring

 Create: /var/www/gema/healthcheck.sh

 - Checks API health endpoint every 5 minutes
 - Auto-restarts if unhealthy
 - Add to crontab: */5 * * * * /var/www/gema/healthcheck.sh

