 Phase 7: Post-Deployment

 7.1 Stripe Webhook Configuration

 1. Stripe Dashboard → Webhooks → Add endpoint
 2. URL: https://yourdomain.com/api/payments/webhook
 3. Events: payment_intent.succeeded, payment_intent.payment_failed, payment_intent.canceled
 4. Copy webhook secret → Update .env → Restart backend

 7.2 Verification Checklist

 # API health
 curl https://yourdomain.com/api/health

 # Frontend loads
 curl -I https://yourdomain.com/

 # PM2 processes
 pm2 status  # Both gema-api and gema-worker online

 # Redis connection
 pm2 logs gema-api | grep "Redis: Connected"

 # MongoDB connection
 pm2 logs gema-api | grep "MongoDB connected"

 # Worker processing
 pm2 logs gema-worker | grep "Workers initialized"

 # SSL valid
 curl -I https://yourdomain.com | grep "HTTP/2 200"

